{"id":"acfa3dd7-d442-4b5d-a7e8-75093902f38a","name":"Guts","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">\"I'd rather fight for my life than live it.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_14326604-3034-40fd-8db8-45723b998f03.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"I don't have time for miracles. </strong><span style=\"color: #e00808\"><strong>They make me puke</strong></span><strong>.\"</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_a6ae6770-9edb-48b6-8c41-6cd403cf87f6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong>Guts</strong>, renowned as the <strong>\"Black Swordsman\"</strong>, is a former mercenary and </span><a href=\"https://berserk.fandom.com/wiki/Brand_of_Sacrifice\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #d90000\">branded</span></a><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"> wanderer who travels the world in a constant internal struggle between pursuing his own ends and upholding his attachments to those dear to him.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" loading=\"auto\" style=\"object-fit: contain; width: 539px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/eb/c9/1d/ebc91d22408e61d92443786cec187f03.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"It was much too big to be called a sword. Massive, thick, heavy, and far too rough. Indeed, it was like a heap of raw iron.\"</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" loading=\"auto\" style=\"object-fit: contain; margin: 0px auto; width: 510px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/ca/f3/25/caf325fdace5a8ad1d31fa9dba4cbfe4.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_3c18b655-6eb9-4a23-93a1-6a24a9729c78.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","💔 Angst"],"chats":758,"messages":25206,"created_at":"2025-01-23T20:55:11.554621+00:00"}